dct_alternative_sm: Liao Ho and Approaches from Entrance to Tienchwangtai including the port of Newchwang (Yingkow)
dct_description_sm: From Chinese I.M.C. Service and Japanese surveys between 1904 and 1909 (with extensive corrections by the Lower Liao River Conservancy Engineers, 1919).
Depths shown by soundings, relief by hachures and spot heights.
Shows drainage, coastal banks, depths, shoals, peaks, Yingkou city plan, marked and unmarked coastal buildings.
